## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-110">Этот конструктор создает пустой <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> экземпляра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-110">This constructor creates an empty <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> instance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-111">Для создания грамматики в пустой <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> экземпляра, добавьте экземпляры классов, представляющих элементы SRGS, такие как <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>, и <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-111">To build a grammar within an empty <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> instance, add instances of classes that represent SRGS elements, such as <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>, and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-112">В следующем примере создается <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> объекта, а затем создает открытое правило с именем `winnerRule`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-112">The following example creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> object and then creates a public rule named `winnerRule`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-113">Затем он создает <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> , включает строку «страны, который выиграл мира по футболу —:» и добавляет этот элемент, чтобы <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Elements%2A> свойства правила.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-113">It then creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> that consists of the string "A nation that has won the world cup is:", and adds this item to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Elements%2A> property of the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-114">Затем в примере создается еще два правила (`ruleEurope` и `ruleSAmerica`), каждая из которых — <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> , содержащий три <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> объектов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-114">The example then creates two more rules (`ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`), each of which is an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object that contains three <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-115">После этого другой <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> создается объект, содержащий <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> объектов, которые ссылаются `ruleEurope` и `ruleSAmerica`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-115">After that, another <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object is created that contains <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> objects that refer to `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-116">Новый <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> объект добавляется в <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Elements%2A> свойство `winnerRule`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-116">The new <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object is then added to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Elements%2A> property of `winnerRule`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-117">После этого все три правила (`winnerRule`, `ruleEurope`, и `ruleSAmerica`) добавляются к <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Rules%2A> свойство <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-117">After this, all three rules (`winnerRule`, `ruleEurope`, and `ruleSAmerica`) are added to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Rules%2A> property of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-118">Наконец три правила компилируются в двоичное представление грамматики.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-118">Finally, the three rules are compiled into a binary representation of the grammar.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
  
  String fileName = Path.GetTempFileName();  
  using (FileStream stream = new FileStream(fileName, FileMode.Create))   
  {   
  
    // Compile the grammar to a binary format.  
    SrgsGrammarCompiler.Compile(document, stream);   
  }  
}  
```

  
  
