## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-201">В следующем примере создается грамматику, которая распознает фразу «страны, который выиграл мира по футболу» следуют страны, который выиграл мира по футболу.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-201">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-202">В примере создается <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> объекта, а затем создает открытое правило с именем `winnerRule`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-202">The example creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> object, and then creates a public rule named `winnerRule`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-203">После добавления строки к правилу `winnerRule`, в примере создается еще два правила (`ruleEurope` и `ruleSAmerica`), каждая из которых содержит список стран.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-203">After adding a string to the rule `winnerRule`, the example creates two more rules (`ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`), each containing a list of countries.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-204">С помощью <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRulesCollection.Add%2A> примеры метода добавляются все три правила (`winnerRule`, `ruleEurope`, и `ruleSAmerica`) для <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Rules%2A> свойство <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-204">Using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRulesCollection.Add%2A> method, the example adds all three rules (`winnerRule`, `ruleEurope`, and `ruleSAmerica`) to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Rules%2A> property of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-213">В следующем примере создается <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> объекта, а затем создает открытое правило с именем `winnerRule`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-213">The following example creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> object, and then creates a public rule named `winnerRule`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-214">Затем он создает <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> , включает строку «страны, который выиграл мира по футболу —:» и добавляет этот элемент, чтобы <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Elements%2A> свойства правила.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-214">It then creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> that consists of the string "A nation that has won the world cup is:", and adds this item to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Elements%2A> property of the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-215">Затем в примере создается еще два правила (`ruleEurope` и `ruleSAmerica`), каждая из которых — <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> , содержащий три <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> объектов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-215">The example then creates two more rules (`ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`), each of which is an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object that contains three <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-216">После этого другой <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> создается объект, содержащий <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> объектов, которые ссылаются `ruleEurope` и `ruleSAmerica`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-216">After that, another <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object is created that contains <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> objects that refer to `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-217">Новый <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> объект добавляется в <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Elements%2A> свойство `winnerRule`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-217">The new <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object is then added to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Elements%2A> property of `winnerRule`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-218">После этого все три правила (`winnerRule`, `ruleEurope`, и `ruleSAmerica`) добавляются к <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Rules%2A> свойство <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-218">After this, all three rules (`winnerRule`, `ruleEurope`, and `ruleSAmerica`) are added to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Rules%2A> property of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-219">Наконец, в примере создается пустой файл XML и экземпляром <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-219">Finally, the example creates an empty XML file and an instance of <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="ac1dc-220"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.WriteSrgs%2A> Использует метод <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> экземпляр для записи содержимого <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> XML-файл.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac1dc-220">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.WriteSrgs%2A> method uses the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> instance to write the contents of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> to the XML file.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
  
  // Create a string object with the path to the file to use.  
  string srgsDocumentFile = Path.Combine(Path.GetTempPath(), "srgsDocumentFile.xml");  
  
  // Create an XmlWriter object and pass the file path.  
  XmlWriter writer = XmlWriter.Create(srgsDocumentFile);  
  
  // Write the contents of the XmlWriter object to an SRGS-compatible XML file.  
  document.WriteSrgs(writer);  
  writer.Close();  
}  
```
